# EmployeeList(employees, skill)
-```
{
    "type": "ColumnSet",
    "columns": [
        {
            "type": "Column",
            "width": "40px",
            "items": []
        },
        {
            "type": "Column",
            "width": "stretch",
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "TextBlock",
                    "text": "Name",
                    "wrap": true,
                    "weight": "Bolder"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "Column",
            "width": "stretch",
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "TextBlock",
                    "text": "Level",
                    "wrap": true,
                    "weight": "Bolder"
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
    "style": "default"
},
{
    "type": "Container",
    "items": [${join(select(employees, e, EmployeeRow(skill, e)), ',')}],
}
```

# EmployeeRow(skill, employee)
- ```
{
    "type": "ColumnSet",
    "columns": [
        {
            "type": "Column",
            "width": "auto",
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "Image",
                    "url": "${if(employee.avatarUrl != null, employee.avatarUrl, BlankAvatar())}",
                    "width": "40px",
                    "height": "40px",
                    "style": "Person"
                }
            ],
            "verticalContentAlignment": "Center"
        },
        {
            "type": "Column",
            "width": "stretch",
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "TextBlock",
                    "text": "${employee.firstName} ${employee.lastName}",
                    "wrap": true
                }
            ],
            "verticalContentAlignment": "Center"
        },
        {
            "type": "Column",
            "width": "stretch",
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "TextBlock",
                    "wrap": true,
                    "text": "${employee.skillLevel}"
                }
            ],
            "verticalContentAlignment": "Center"
        }
    ],
    "height": "stretch",
    "separator": true
}
```

